% OECD Structural Analysis Database
% Frequently Asked Questions
% April 2014

# Measuring value-added along global production networks

##### A Global production network
- CZE(VA, INT goods) $\Rightarrow$ DEU(INT goods) $\Rightarrow \Rightarrow \Rightarrow$ CHN(final goods) $\Rightarrow$ USA(final consumption)

##### Current TiVA FDDVA (VA created by foreign final demand)
- CZE(VA) $\Rightarrow \Rightarrow \Rightarrow \Rightarrow \Rightarrow$ USA (Final consumption)

##### Current TiVA EXGR_FVA (Foreign valued added embodied in exports)
- CZE(VA) $\Rightarrow \Rightarrow \Rightarrow$CHN(final goods)$\Rightarrow$ World

# Frequently requested TiVA indicators regarding regional integration
  1. CZE(VA) $\Rightarrow$ DEU(INT goods) $\Rightarrow$ CHN(final goods) $\Rightarrow$ World
  2. CZE(VA) $\Rightarrow$ DEU(INT goods) $\Rightarrow$ $\Rightarrow
     \Rightarrow$ USA (final consumption)
<!--- CHN(INT EX) $\Rightarrow$ DEU(FNL goods) $\Rightarrow$
     $\Rightarrow \Rightarrow$ USA (HH FNL) --->
- Many country pairs are not interesting in general e.g. VA involved in the production network of CZE $\Rightarrow$ KHM $\Rightarrow$ CYP $\Rightarrow$ CHL

# Currently developed tools

- [stanapp](http://10.101.26.220:3838/stanapp/) STAN data browsing tool
- [stanindici4](http://10.101.26.220:3838/stanindici4/) STAN indicator (ISIC4)
- [icioapp](http://10.101.26.220:3838/icioapp/) TiVA indicator
- [icioappedit](http://10.101.26.220:3838/icioappedit/) TiVA indicator (with editing functionality)

## Future additions
- Other embodied indicators (jobs/co2 vectors)
- BTDIxE browser
- Interactive charts

